            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-900 mb-4">
              Fire Door Maintenance
            </h3>
            <p class="text-brand-600 leading-relaxed">
              Regular maintenance services to keep your fire doors in optimal
              condition. We ensure doors continue to function properly and
              maintain their fire resistance rating.
