                  <p class="text-brand-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Established Coulsy Ltd, working on high-end residential and
                    commercial projects, perfecting traditional joinery
                    techniques and modern construction methods.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
